
# Islands in the Sky

A story of a young man who lives on a space station.

=> islands_in_the_sky.gmi
=> ../../index.gmi

> I have never known Earth. I have only known the stars.

> This space station is my home. My world.

> But I dream of Earth. Of green fields and blue oceans.

> And one day, I will go there. I will see the world of my ancestors.

> And I will find my place in the universe.

> ...a journey of self-discovery...
